<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,787,1207]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1004,1028]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="H. Milne Edwards" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[324,544,1004,1028]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aspera">
<emphasis box="[324,544,1004,1028]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Schizophrys aspera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been first recorded by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nobili, G." box="[861,1029,1004,1028]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="13 - 159" refId="ref51383" refString="Nobili, G. (1906 a) Crustaces decapodes et stomatopodes. In: Mission J. Bonnier et Ch. Perez (Golfe Persique, 1901). Bulletin Scientifique de la France et de la Belgique, 40, 13 - 159, pls. 2 - 7." type="journal article" year="1906">Nobili (1906a)</bibRefCitation>
from the Persian Gulf in the 
<collectingCountry box="[1371,1432,1004,1028]" name="United Arab Emirates" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">UAE</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Tirmizi, N. M. &amp; Kazmi, Q. B." box="[151,440,1039,1063]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="135 - 141" refId="ref53266" refString="Tirmizi, N. M. &amp; Kazmi, Q. B. (1995) A new species of Schizophrys from Pakistan with a note on Schizophrys aspera (Crustacea: Decapoda: Majidae). In: Thompson, M. - F. &amp; Tirmizi, N. M. (eds.): The Arabian Sea - Living marine resources and the environment. Oxford &amp; IBH Publishing Co., New Delhi, 135 - 141." type="book chapter" year="1995">Tirmizi &amp; Kazmi (1995)</bibRefCitation>
described a new species of the genus, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tirmizi &amp; Q. B. Kazmi" authorityYear="1995" box="[912,1210,1040,1064]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pakistanensis">
<emphasis box="[912,1210,1040,1064]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Schizophrys pakistanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from the 
<collectingCountry box="[1341,1436,1039,1063]" name="Pakistan" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
waters, which is very similar to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="H. Milne Edwards" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[508,612,1076,1100]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aspera">
<emphasis box="[508,522,1076,1100]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[536,612,1077,1100]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">aspera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Apel, M." box="[626,761,1076,1100]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref45060" refString="Apel, M. (2001) Taxonomie und Zoogeographie der Brachyura, Paguridea und Porcellanidae (Crustacea: Decapoda) des Persisch-Arabischen Golfes. Unpublished doctoral thesis, Johann Wolfgang Goethe-Universitat, Frankfurt a. M., 268 pp." type="book" year="2001">Apel (2001)</bibRefCitation>
collected 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tirmizi &amp; Q. B. Kazmi" authorityYear="1995" box="[876,1055,1076,1100]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pakistanensis">
<emphasis box="[876,890,1076,1100]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[904,1055,1076,1100]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">pakistanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the Saudi Arabian coast and discussed that more probably the record of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="H. Milne Edwards" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[638,742,1112,1136]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aspera">
<emphasis box="[638,652,1112,1136]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[666,742,1113,1136]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">aspera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Basson, P. W. &amp; Burchard, J. E. &amp; Hardy, J. T. &amp; Price, A. R. G." box="[785,1012,1111,1136]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" refId="ref45702" refString="Basson, P. W., Burchard, J. E., Hardy, J. T. &amp; Price, A. R. G. (1977) Biotopes of the Western Arabian Gulf: Marine life and environments of Saudi Arabia. ARAMCO, Dept. of Loss Prevention and environmental affairs, Dhahran: 289 pp." type="book" year="1977">
Basson 
<emphasis box="[874,923,1112,1136]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">et al</emphasis>
. (1977)
</bibRefCitation>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[1081,1228,1111,1135]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
could be assigned to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tirmizi &amp; Q. B. Kazmi" authorityYear="1995" box="[180,359,1148,1172]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pakistanensis">
<emphasis box="[180,194,1148,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[208,359,1148,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">pakistanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. We did not collect 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tirmizi &amp; Q. B. Kazmi" authorityYear="1995" box="[586,765,1148,1172]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pakistanensis">
<emphasis box="[586,600,1148,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[614,765,1148,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">pakistanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
during the present study, whereas the record of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="H. Milne Edwards" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[1305,1410,1148,1172]" class="Malacostraca" family="Majidae" genus="Schizophrys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aspera">
<emphasis box="[1305,1319,1148,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1334,1410,1149,1172]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">aspera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is new to the Iranian coast.
</paragraph>
